title: The Shadow of Summerhall: Aerys & Rhaegar (2015)
description:
This episode delves deep into Aerys, Rhaegar and other characters who were impacted by Summerhall. There's talk of how the Mad King could wreak havoc on the Seven Kingdoms even now... Published August 26, 2015.
